@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
title Governance action lifecycle

[*] --> Live : proposed on-chain\nwith a refundable deposit

Live : bodies vote for
Live : govActionLifetime (6 epochs on mainnet)

Live --> Ratified : thresholds met for its type
Live --> Expired : lifetime elapses\nwithout meeting thresholds

Ratified : added to the enactment set\nat the epoch boundary
Ratified --> Enacted : next epoch boundary\nchange takes effect

Expired --> [*] : deposit returned
Enacted --> [*] : deposit returned

note right of Live
  Deposit is returned to the proposer's
  reward account once the action leaves
  the Live state (ratified or expired).
end note
@enduml
